<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.280576>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Leviapseudes macaronesia n. sp., holotype, female. Holotype. A, lateral view. scale bar 1 mm. B, antennule. B 1, same, apex. C, antenna. D, labrum. E, left mandible. F, right mandible. G, labium. H, maxillule. I, maxilla. J, maxilliped. K, same, endite. L, epignath. Scale bars 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/280576/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.280577>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Leviapseudes macaronesia n. sp., holotype, female. A, cheliped. B, pereopod 1. C, pereopod 2. C 1, same, apical seta. D, pereopod 3. E, Pereopod 4. E 1, same, propodus / dactylus, scale bar 0.1 mm. F, pereopod 5. G, pereopod 6. Scale bars pereopods 1 mm. H, pleopod, scale bar 0.5 mm. I, uropod, scale bar 0.1 mm. J, attached ciliate, scale bar 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/280577/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

